    "# M365 Copilot Chat Integration\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook implements a secure, interactive chat interface for M365 Copilot (via MS Graph API) using the Azure SDK for Python.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Features:\n",
    "- Secure `.env` configuration loading.\n",
    "- Azure AD Authentication using `azure-identity`.\n",
    "- MS Graph API integration for Chat interactions.\n",
    "- Unit tests for core logic.\n",
    "- Interactive Chat UI."
   ]
  },
